    "description_long": "This object is a compact, modern submachine gun with a matte black finish, featuring a streamlined, minimalist design. The body is constructed primarily from metal, with a fixed, solid stock extending from the rear for shoulder support. The grip and trigger assembly are ergonomically shaped, and a curved box magazine is inserted just ahead of the trigger guard. The barrel is short and cylindrical, with a simple muzzle and no visible attachments or cooling features. Iron sights are present, with a fixed front post and a rear notch, providing basic aiming capability.",
